    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一度风光无限的矮人文明如今尘埃遍地，只剩流亡者和盘踞的怪物在此盘踞。你将作为孤独的矮人，开始一场满是探索与砍杀的RPG冒险之旅，为矮人同族重建家园，并探究祖先留下的奥秘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地形多样，任你探索</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375750/extras/4c754d5bdc04046efa695e7d9c5d95b6.poster.avif?t=1768224183\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375750/extras/4c754d5bdc04046efa695e7d9c5d95b6.webm?t=1768224183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >矮人的故土辽阔、富饶、地形多样，有忠心耿耿的盟友，也潜藏着虎视眈眈的敌人。在追求财富与真相的旅途中，你将穿过繁茂的植被，应对风云莫测的天气，探索发光水晶洞穴等各种环境。誓将矮人赶尽杀绝的敌人前赴后继而来，准备好迎战，杀出一条血路吧。   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >矮人社群，亟待重建</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375750/extras/afbbbffc7faee7ad0fefb5ceaa96b8c6.poster.avif?t=1768224183\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375750/extras/afbbbffc7faee7ad0fefb5ceaa96b8c6.webm?t=1768224183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >旅途上，你会遇到落难的矮人盟友。伸出援手，与他们齐心协力共建文明，为族人创造一片安全的避风港。收集各类资源、结识有一技之长的冒险者，还有机会解锁全新的设施和技术，不断推动你的重建之路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >专属风格，由你做主</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375750/extras/43ac3dcc76493c7047d1dadf177b17ed.poster.avif?t=1768224183\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375750/extras/43ac3dcc76493c7047d1dadf177b17ed.webm?t=1768224183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索、实验一系列武器、装备和技能树，从外貌到战斗风格，全面定制你的矮人英雄。是单枪匹马直入敌阵，还是绕到落单哥布林背后发动奇袭？每场战斗皆由你掌控。只不过，千万牢记——敌人也会适应你的行动，战斗时务必保持警惕。 </p>",
